events.name: Cloud Study Jam 2019
events.description:
Google Cloud Study Jam 2019 is here!
We're super excited to announce the first edition of CSJ ! Join our jam immediately and get official Google training!

With a Cloud Study Jam, you will learn the fundamental tools and capabilities of Google Cloud. Developers will be able to get hands-on experience with Docker, Kubernetes and Scientific Data Processing.

Together we'll work through several Google Cloud Platform Essentials labs, then you will get free access to the next quest so you can finish this series of labs.

Make sure to bring your laptops and chargers since this will be a totally hands-on event. The labs will run on all of the latest versions of the popular browsers.

Agenda: Coming Soon!

Venue: University Of Bordj Bou Arreridj

Time: 11 AM - 2 PM

events.name: Cloud Next Extended'19
events.description:
This time Google Developers Group Community, BBA presents you the most exciting event for June 2019: Cloudnext Extended 2019!

Most awaited event of the year . Where we will be reviewing various intriguing cloud technologies introduced at the Google CloudNext event held at San Francisco.

So get ready to witness some of our expert speakers who will be conducting a variety of sessions on different areas of cloud-related technologies .

Book a seat : https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSclh_q0kIWQGToI1ykg-rZPK96IFPc0ENfw_vC9lbRmP-Wz4Q/viewform

events.name: #I am Remarkable

venue.name: Centre de Loisirs Scientifiques (CLS) CLS Benhala Ali - BBA

events.description:
I am remarkable is a google initiative empowering women and underrepresented groups to celebrate their achievements in the workplace and beyond.
Our goal is to improve the self promotion motivation and skills of women and underrepresented groups
In addition to challenging the social perception arround self promotion.
I am remarkable workshop is going to be lead by Mebarkia Houria.
In addition to that, we are going to hold a public speaking workshop by Fatima Lilia Meklout
This session is in collaboration with Youth Unity Association.
The session is going to start at 9:30
Bring your motivation, your stories, and your aspirations in life.
